Reasoning: The paper discusses the simplifying effects of high-dimensional datasets on machine learning and neuroscience, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the mention of "high-dimensional representations of reality" and "high-dimensional brain" suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also mentions applications of machine learning in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), which further supports these sub-categories. Finally, the mention of "simplifying effects" may suggest a connection to control systems (cs.SY).
